            NatigaEmt7an Project – Exam Results Management System.
        </h2>
        <div>
            🔧 <strong>Project Structure</strong>
        </div>

        <div class="ms-2">
            <strong>NatigaEmt7an.Api</strong><br />
            Contains Web API controllers<br />
            Handles all backend logic and HTTP endpoints<br />
            Exposes functionalities like viewing student results, ranking, and statistics<br /><br />

            <strong>NatigaEmt7an.Blazor</strong><br />
            Client-side Blazor WebAssembly application<br />
            Provides an interactive UI for students and users to view results<br />
            Responsive design with intuitive navigation<br /><br />

            <strong>NatigaEmt7an.Contracts</strong><br />
            Contains Data Transfer Objects (DTOs) shared between the API and frontend<br />
            Ensures consistent data exchange and separation of concerns<br /><br />
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

