            📄 <strong>Pages Overview</strong>
        </div>

        <div class="ms-2">
            <strong>Home.razor</strong><br />
            Allows users to search for students by <strong>name</strong> or <strong>seat number</strong>.<br />
            Results are displayed with <strong>pagination</strong> for better navigation and performance.<br /><br />

            <strong>TopStudents.razor</strong><br />
            Users can select filters such as <strong>Governorate</strong>, <strong>School Administration</strong>, and <strong>School</strong>.<br />
            Displays the <strong>top 50 students</strong> based on total grades from the selected region.<br /><br />

            <strong>StudentStatistics.razor</strong><br />
            Allows filtering by <strong>Governorate</strong>, <strong>School Administration</strong>, and <strong>School</strong>.<br />
            Generates graphical reports showing <strong>grade distribution</strong> and the <strong>number of students grouped by grade</strong>.<br /><br />

            <strong>StudentDetails.razor</strong><br />
            Displays full details of a specific student, including <strong>grades, status, and academic performance</strong>.<br />
            Provides an in-depth view of the student’s result breakdown.<br /><br />
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


